{"tid":2233317,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（新發明）中国一款智慧男用貞操帶證實可被黑客入侵從遠端「封鎖」","createTime":"2020-10-07T04:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T05:51:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"71949954db9905a0d203ad73f01809d456accb55","tid":2233317,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/10/07/1/8701663.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=465\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F10%2F07%2F1%2F8701663.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D465&h=9b876ccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國資安公司 Pen Test Partners 發現這款中國的智慧男性貞操帶 API 設計有非常多缺陷，駭客可以輕易駭進，遠端把貞操帶永久性鎖起來！<br />\n<br />\nCellmate Chastity Cage 是一款專為 BDSM 族群所設計，具備連網能力可以用 APP 解鎖的「智慧男性貞操帶」，依照使用者設定，可以將穿戴者生殖器的「生殺大權」交給另外一個夥伴。不過這款男用貞操帶被爆出有著致命的資安問題。<br />\n<br />\n英國資安公司 Pen Test Partners 發現 Cellmate Chastity Cage 的 API 設計有非常多缺陷，導致駭客可以很輕易的駭進 APP 裡，遠端把貞操帶永久性鎖起來！不只如此，駭客還可以從 API 裡輕易的獲得使用者的私人訊息和地理定位資訊。<br />\n<br />\n而且這款貞操帶的設計比較特別，表面是氯丁橡膠塗層的聚碳酸酯，並且用一個特殊的鋅合金卡環扣住陰囊（但有開口可以小便），它沒有像是實體鑰匙或手動按鈕等其他物理性的解法，所以只能用切割機、螺栓鉗，或是用過載電壓讓電路板短路等危險性極高的暴力手法打開它....<br />\n<br />\n這是一款中國設計、中國製造的產品，生產商為廣州佛山的「囚愛 QIUI」；而且在被證實可以駭客攻擊之前，這款貞操帶 APP 的評價就十分糟糕，經常「當機」無法順利解鎖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/10/07/1/8701662.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F10%2F07%2F1%2F8701662.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D400&h=9abd8aa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPen Test Partners 的資安人員也說，他們在 4 月份就發現了 API 漏洞並且跟囚愛報告，雖然他們在 6 月份更新了貞操帶的 APP 以修復該漏洞，但還是有非常多的使用者未更新；此外囚愛曾向美媒保證 8 月份會在全面更新一次，但至今並未實現。囚愛現在的麻煩是，如果它完全禁用舊的 API 的確能修復漏洞，但可能把所有尚未更新 APP 的貞操帶上鎖，反而更糟。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7086/4916537\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7086%2F4916537&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmSMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=0037f996\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7086/4916537</a>"},{"pid":"79cde11f2e376a003a1c90417377cd6293d589fe","tid":2233317,"uid":78046,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:53:49.000Z","msg":"它沒有像是實體鑰匙或手動按鈕等其他物理性的解法，所以只能用切<span class=\"red\">割機、螺栓鉗</span>，或是用過載電壓讓電路板短路等危險性極高的暴力手法打開它.... <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37794e6e1c8667ae9ee9b420c5ae2fb1e5798a68","tid":2233317,"uid":50744,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:14:22.000Z","msg":"遲早所有已婚男士都會法定要帶呢啲"},{"pid":"d7070006d24f9d1e44a217dbc85ef83bf116a99f","tid":2233317,"uid":34409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37794e6e1c8667ae9ee9b420c5ae2fb1e5798a68","tid":2233317,"uid":50744,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:14:22.000Z","msg":"遲早所有已婚男士都會法定要帶呢啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:17:08.000Z","msg":"有GPS定位，應該係所有香港出世既人都要戴"},{"pid":"182d95936cfe1e0340e48c42d6915ae5e02572d8","tid":2233317,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcT5T5rM1keG3-Gx2VS1QaWNXoA2PvvCoIBtTQ&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcT5T5rM1keG3-Gx2VS1QaWNXoA2PvvCoIBtTQ%26usqp%3DCAU&h=9a26c059&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a95ceb720fe623a749618785e4b7b9d37aac10cc","tid":2233317,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"